These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, asparagus, pumpkin, avocado
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, hip-hop, r&b, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: french, argentine, british, american
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, goat, ferret
 1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
 3. the french is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the british is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the argentine is the person eating pumpkin##1
 8. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the ferret and the fan of salsa##2
10. the person eating peach is the owner of the ferret##1
11. the fan of r&b is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | pumpkin  | peach    | avocado    | asparagus   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | punk   | r&b       | salsa    |
| Nationality   | argentine | french | american    | british |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | ferret       | bird | goat     |

