.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, cucumber, pumpkin, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, writing, cooking, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, american, egyptian, argentine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rugby, baseball, cricket, snowboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
 2. the american is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is the brazilian##1
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 7. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 8. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
 9. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4
11. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | strawberry  | cucumber    | pumpkin     | lettuce       |
| Hobby         | cooking | chess | traveling   | writing |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian   | american   | argentine    |
| Sport         | cricket | snowboarding  | rugby | baseball   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, tea, soy-milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, chef, journalist, architect
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, australian, canadian, thai
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, cat, chinchilla
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the bartender##3
 2. the australian is the journalist##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 4. the bartender is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the person drinking water is the architect##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is the thai##1
 8. the architect is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left of the nigerian##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking tea##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | tea   | soy-milk    | water      |
| Job           | journalist | bartender | chef | architect     |
| Nationality   | australian      | thai   | nigerian   | canadian |
| Pet           | chinchilla         | rabbit       | cat  | turtle       |

