.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, 7up, juice
There 4 different types of food: mango, strawberry, cherry, lettuce
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, writing, video-games, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, rowing, swimming, baseball
 1. the person drinking cola is the person eating mango##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 3. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is writing##1
10. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the person drinking 7up is the person eating lettuce##1
12. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | juice       | 7up   | cola   | milk   |
| Food       | strawberry        | lettuce | mango    | cherry       |
| Hobby      | dancing | writing    | video-games  | skydiving |
| Sport      | rowing  | swimming  | sailing | baseball    |

