.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, eggplant, radish, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, cooking, filmmaking, puzzles
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, dancer, freelancer, fisherman
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball, badminton, rowing
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person eating garlic##2
 3. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the dancer is the person eating papaya##1
 5. the scientist is on the left or right of the dancer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating eggplant is the scientist##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the dancer##1
 9. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the dancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
11. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
12. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | radish    | garlic      | papaya          | eggplant    |
| Hobby   | cooking | puzzles       | filmmaking | hiking |
| Job     | fisherman     | freelancer      | dancer     | scientist |
| Sport   | basketball   | rowing | badminton        | biathlon   |

