.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola, water, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, tomato, cranberry, carrot
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, jazz, funk, blues
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, nigerian, japanese, indonesian
 1. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of blues is between the japanese and the fan of jazz##2
 7. the fan of funk is the person eating cranberry##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the person eating cranberry##1
 9. the nigerian is on the far right##1
10. the egyptian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage      | water  | cola    | fanta       | mirinda       |
| Food          | carrot    | cranberry | tomato | pineapple     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | funk        | blues    | jazz   |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | japanese      | indonesian    | nigerian |

