.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, superhero, crime, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, chinese, brazilian, spanish
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hedgehog, turtle, goldfish
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, tram, bus, van
 1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 2. the spanish is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 4. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the thai##3
 5. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 6. the brazilian is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 9. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
10. the chinese is on the far right##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
12. the owner of the rabbit is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | crime    | comedy  | satire      |
| Nationality   | thai      | brazilian | spanish | chinese   |
| Pet           | turtle       | goldfish | rabbit   | hedgehog       |
| Transport     | van      | bus | car  | tram |

