The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, musical, martial-arts, action
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, argentine, indonesian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goat, pony
 1. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the pony and the owner of the goat##2
 3. the polish is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the egyptian is on the right of the indonesian##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the argentine##1
 9. the owner of the fish is between the polish and the person watching musical movies##2
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | reading    | singing    | hiking |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | superhero       | musical  | action    |
| Nationality   | polish | argentine | indonesian | egyptian   |
| Pet           | goat    | fish        | pony   | frog    |

