The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, metal, hip-hop, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, swimming, ice-hockey, biathlon
 1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of trance is between the person watching zombie movies and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person watching zombie movies##1
 9. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of metal is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
13. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
