The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, teacher, journalist, electrician
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, malaysian, canadian, american
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rowing, swimming, skiing
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the teacher is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is golf##2
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the american##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking water##1
 6. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 8. the american is on the right of the canadian##1
 9. the electrician is on the left of the teacher##1
10. the coach is in an even position##4
11. the spanish is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Beverage      | water      | soy-milk      | fanta           | sprite |
| Job           | electrician | teacher | journalist | coach        |
| Nationality   | canadian      | american  | spanish          | malaysian      |
| Sport         | skiing       | swimming    | golf       | rowing       |

