The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, jet-ski, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 2. the person eating papaya is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 4. the person eating potato is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the van##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person eating potato is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person driving the van##1
11. the person eating nectarine is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |
