The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, social-worker, security-guard, scientist
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, tennis, cycling, baseball
 1. the scientist is in an odd position##4
 2. the scientist is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
 3. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the nurse##3
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the security-guard##2
 5. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating asparagus is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 9. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
12. the nurse is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
13. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |   3    |     4      |
