 7. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
 8. the paramedic is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
10. the firefighter is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the doctor is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

