 6. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
 8. the dutch is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 9. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4
10. the fan of folk is between the person watching thriller movies and the brazilian##2
11. the thai is on the right of the fan of folk##1
12. the dutch is on the left or right of the thai##3

.:: Answer ::.
