.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, soy-milk, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, traveling, gardening, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, horror, superhero, adventure
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, handball, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
11. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is camping is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk       | cola | coffee        | sprite        |
| Hobby         | fishing | gardening       | camping | traveling |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror        | zombie    | superhero      |
| Sport         | climbing     | handball    | surfing | lacrosse   |

