.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, folk, trance, disco
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese, british, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, baseball, surfing, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, trike, train
 1. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is surfing is between the pakistani and the malaysian##2
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the chinese##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 6. the fan of folk is the person who's sport is baseball##1
 7. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 8. the malaysian is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
10. the pakistani is in an even position##4
11. the pakistani is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is on the right of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | folk      | salsa | disco     | trance        |
| Nationality   | british | malaysian  | chinese     | pakistani |
| Sport         | baseball    | tennis | surfing      | skiing |
| Transport     | train | ship     | trike | bus       |

 